author: mherndon
msg: An experimental branch for lucene.net 4 which maps to lucene 4.  This will serve to prototype changes to the project without messing with the current trunk or 2.9.4g branch.  This branch uses the portable library tools, nuget, style cop, gallio & nunit, sandcastle, fxcop.  This will give people an opportunity to see what the default styles are for style cop, fx cop, etc.
